text: Marc Deuquet (16 October 1933 - 18 December 2009) was a French equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:2009 deaths Category:French male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
